  <title>GWeather.TemperatureUnit</title>
  <p>The measure unit to use for temperature values, when retrieved by
the <link xref="GWeather.Info.get_value_temp"/> family of functions.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>TemperatureUnit.INVALID</code></title>
  <p>invalid unit</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>TemperatureUnit.DEFAULT</code></title>
  <p>the user preferred temperature unit</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>TemperatureUnit.KELVIN</code></title>
  <p>Kelvin (absolute) temperature scale</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>TemperatureUnit.CENTIGRADE</code></title>
  <p>Celsius temperature scale</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>TemperatureUnit.FAHRENHEIT</code></title>
